    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是 Puyo Puyo 的粉丝还是拼图街机的粉丝？让自己沉浸在五彩缤纷的梅奥梅奥世界中，灵感来自快餐、酱汁和调味品。在这款 Match-4 拼图中玩蓝色、芥末酱、蛋黄酱、芥末酱和番茄酱，这将考验你的反应能力和聪明才智。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款 Match-4 拼图中，掌握各种连击来制造爆炸链和毁灭性攻击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索专为所有玩家特征设计的 4 种游戏模式：拼图、训练、生存和多人游戏。无论你是经验丰富的竞争对手还是想要按照自己的节奏探索游戏的新手，每个人都能找到适合自己的东西。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在本地或在线挑战来自世界各地的朋友或玩家。与最多 4 名玩家同时畅玩比赛。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对您的个人资料进行个性化设置，解锁一系列既可爱又疯狂的头像</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228550/extras/e72a41a00556fd6d955f8faa3332f00c.poster.avif?t=1749111318\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228550/extras/e72a41a00556fd6d955f8faa3332f00c.webm?t=1749111318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228550/extras/e72a41a00556fd6d955f8faa3332f00c.mp4?t=1749111318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用拼图模式，获得壮观的连击。通过 160 个渐进难度级别来提高你的思维和反应能力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228550/extras/02f58b4c011cd3c55884e2d9665e186e.poster.avif?t=1749111318\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228550/extras/02f58b4c011cd3c55884e2d9665e186e.webm?t=1749111318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228550/extras/02f58b4c011cd3c55884e2d9665e186e.mp4?t=1749111318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与来自世界各地的玩家或朋友一起沉浸在在线或本地多人游戏中。为最多 4 名玩家创建公共或私人游戏。你也可以面对所有级别的人工智能来进步，但要小心，它们不会给你带来任何好处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228550/extras/05ad66ec00f9219dbd24e459333e5286.poster.avif?t=1749111318\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228550/extras/05ad66ec00f9219dbd24e459333e5286.webm?t=1749111318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228550/extras/05ad66ec00f9219dbd24e459333e5286.mp4?t=1749111318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对唱片充满热情？生存模式及其3个难度级别为您提供无尽的体验，挑战您并突破极限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228550/extras/c9183e2e3ae2487f75911df33e3a326c.poster.avif?t=1749111318\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228550/extras/c9183e2e3ae2487f75911df33e3a326c.webm?t=1749111318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228550/extras/c9183e2e3ae2487f75911df33e3a326c.mp4?t=1749111318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >训练模式允许你激活各种设置来帮助你提高技能。花点时间来探索这个易于学习但很难掌握的游戏！</p>",
